{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1975,"month":12,"day":14}],"page_start":3,"page_end":3,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"反坦克演练剪影（二首）","authors":["李存葆"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"伏击"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暗夜如墨静悄悄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千百雄兵卧堑壕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫道此时寂无声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"且听惊雷爆！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侧耳听，“敌”坦克隆隆响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似闻豺狼声声嗥；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仔细看，“敌”坦克结成群，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如见北极熊伸魔爪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧紧腰间的反坦克雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摸摸胸前的炸药包，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手怒握爆破筒啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此时象在珍宝鸟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半圆形的阵地似大网，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撒网只待“乌龟”到。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月牙状的堑壕如巨弓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"利箭在弦早搭好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"近了，“敌”坦克近了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇士屏住呼吸，压住心跳；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"近了，“敌”坦克近了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"健儿双眼紧盯，不慌不躁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"默念炸药包啊，莫心急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"且将那满腔怒焰心头烧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等等，等“敌”坦克来到你面前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你便可将“乌龟”炸倒！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细嘱爆破筒啊，莫心焦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"且将那万钧雷霆胸中包。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等等，等“敌”坦克栽进陷阱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你即可将雷声化做捷报！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，一声号令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唤来惊雷遍野，飓风呼啸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看呀，看阵地前燃起堆堆冲天火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把祖国的夜装点得多美多娇……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士——穿甲弹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明晃晃，沉甸甸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一排排的穿甲弹；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粗胳臂，黑红脸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一队队的英雄汉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿甲弹——战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士—一穿甲弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"性格相同，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一样肝胆！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级文化大革命中淬火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"批林批孔中锤锻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的嘱托胸中装啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与侵略者不共戴天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是铁——咱敢碰！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是钢——咱敢穿！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声令下杀出膛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为胜利，粉身碎骨也心甘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，一个战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一道钢铁的防线；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，一发炮弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一座焚敌的火山……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"针锋相对 王建华作（图片）"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"批林批孔","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}